Luck Charm resembles a Four Leaf Clover on a Red Or Purple Leather Band.

Make Clovers spawn in Chests in dungeons. Check loot tables appropriate for Clovers.
Make Charms spawn in Nether Bastions, Or Strongholds. Or perhaps Piglin trade.

Compact Clovers in a Sack. Credit vectorwing for the texture of Sack.
Villager (CLERIC) buys Luck Charms for 34 Emeralds Or 4 Blocks of Emerald (36 Emeralds)

